1
00:02:27,970 --> 00:02:29,620
我是总统
This is the president.

2
00:02:29,970 --> 00:02:32,430
-让康威接电话  -你要跟我说话
- Put on Conway. - You will speak to me.

3
00:02:32,430 --> 00:02:34,320
不  我们只跟他谈  否则挂断
No, we only talk to him or we hang up.

4
00:02:35,030 --> 00:02:38,420
听到直升机了吗  还有狗吠
Do you hear the helicopters yet? Or the dogs?

5
00:02:38,950 --> 00:02:41,460
我们接近了  很快就能找到你
We're getting closer and we will find you.

6
00:02:41,460 --> 00:02:43,800
唯一的问题是  我们抓到你们之前
The only question is will you work with us 

7
00:02:43,800 --> 00:02:45,300
你们是否愿意合作
before we get there?

8
00:02:45,300 --> 00:02:48,130
赎金和撤军都别指望了
The money's not happening and neither is the military withdrawal.

9
00:02:48,130 --> 00:02:49,980
但你够聪明  早就知道
But you're smart enough to know that.

10
00:02:49,980 --> 00:02:52,210
重点在于艾哈迈德
The objective here is Ahmadi,

11
00:02:52,210 --> 00:02:54,020
这是我想谈的
and that's what I'd like to discuss.

12
00:02:54,020 --> 00:02:54,890
选择权在你
Well, the choice is yours.

13
00:02:54,890 --> 00:02:57,280
你要么满足我们的要求  要么不满足
You either meet our demands or you don't.

14
00:03:00,660 --> 00:03:04,160
我昨晚跟康威州长深谈过
I spoke at length last night with Governor Conway.

15
00:03:04,160 --> 00:03:06,830
我今早本想无视你的电话
I was of a mind to ignore your call this morning,

16
00:03:06,830 --> 00:03:09,470
但他说服我继续跟你沟通
but he convinced me that we should keep talking.

17
00:03:09,470 --> 00:03:11,420
是吧  州长
Isn't that right, Governor?

18
00:03:12,510 --> 00:03:15,570
-我只想寻求和平解决方案  -我也是
- I just want a peaceful resolution. - As do I.

19
00:03:15,570 --> 00:03:18,680
你想叫上州长  我想叫上艾哈迈德
You wanted to include the Governor, I want to include Ahmadi.

20
00:03:18,680 --> 00:03:21,970
-你是在拖延  -你不想跟你的领袖说话吗
- You're trying to stall. - You refusing to speak to your leader?

21
00:03:22,340 --> 00:03:23,440
他在线吗
Is he on now?

22
00:03:23,440 --> 00:03:26,060
你释放米勒一家  我们就让他跟你通话
You release the Millers, then we put him on.

23
00:03:26,060 --> 00:03:28,700
不  你无权谈条件
No, you don't get to dictate terms.

24
00:03:28,700 --> 00:03:31,470
你表现出诚意  我们才会还以诚意
We show good will when you show good will.

25
00:03:32,430 --> 00:03:35,320
我给你10秒钟重新考虑
I'm giving you ten seconds to reconsider your position.

26
00:03:35,330 --> 00:03:37,580
之后  我们就切断电话
After that, we disconnect the call.

27
00:03:37,580 --> 00:03:39,690
真主的旨意  我们会杀了他们
Insha'Allah. We'll kill them.

28
00:03:41,240 --> 00:03:43,310
10秒钟  现在开始
Ten seconds, starting now.

29
00:03:48,150 --> 00:03:49,590
5秒钟
Five seconds.

30
00:03:53,860 --> 00:03:56,440
-结束通话  -一个人质
- End the call. - One hostage.

31
00:03:56,440 --> 00:03:58,350
-三个  -一个
- All three. - One.

32
00:03:58,350 --> 00:04:00,270
把女儿和母亲交出来
Give us the daughter and the mother.

33
00:04:00,270 --> 00:04:01,670
不  女孩我们要留下
No, we keep the girl.

34
00:04:02,530 --> 00:04:05,320
你已经两次打通了
You managed to get the president of the United States on the phone

35
00:04:05,330 --> 00:04:07,110
美国总统的电话
not once, but twice.

36
00:04:07,110 --> 00:04:09,260
你得释放女儿和母亲
You will release the daughter and the mother

37
00:04:09,260 --> 00:04:10,980
否则我再也不会与你联络了
or you will never hear from me again,

38
00:04:10,980 --> 00:04:13,730
而且你会失去与你领袖通话的机会
and you will lose your chance to speak to your leader.

39
00:04:13,730 --> 00:04:15,140
马上说
Tell me now.

40
00:04:19,550 --> 00:04:21,080
他们挂线了  先生
They've disconnected, sir.

41
00:04:34,880 --> 00:04:35,810
停下
Stop.

42
00:04:43,510 --> 00:04:44,730
艾哈迈德先生
Mr. Ahmadi.

43
00:04:47,050 --> 00:04:50,820
你可以在楼上洗澡  衣柜里有干净衣服
You can shower upstairs. There's fresh clothes in the closet.

44
00:05:32,180 --> 00:05:33,360
只有参联会主席和护送他的
The only people who know are the Chairman

45
00:05:33,370 --> 00:05:34,400
海豹突击队队员知道
and the SEALs who escorted him.

46
00:05:34,400 --> 00:05:37,170
-通话线路安全吗  -直通总统办公室
- Do we have a secure line? - Direct to the Oval.

47
00:05:38,350 --> 00:05:39,600
总统先生
Mr. President...

48
00:05:41,910 --> 00:05:44,960
换了我绝不会同意把艾哈迈德扯进来
I would have never condoned bringing Ahmadi into this.

49
00:05:44,970 --> 00:05:46,910
幸好  我做决定的依据
Well, lucky for me, I'm not making decisions

50
00:05:46,910 --> 00:05:49,450
不是你会同意什么
based on what you would or would not condone.

51
00:05:49,450 --> 00:05:52,440
等着我告诉媒体你把话强加于我
Watch me tell the press you put words in my mouth.

52
00:05:52,950 --> 00:05:54,050
随意
Feel free.

53
00:05:54,310 --> 00:05:57,650
但我觉得他们不太可能会相信你
I think they'll have a hard time believing you, though.

54
00:05:57,650 --> 00:06:01,340
看看你的信息  你的手下肯定一直在给你发邮件
Check your messages. I'm sure your staff's been emailing you.

55
00:06:02,510 --> 00:06:05,510
安排车送州长和他家人去机场
Arrange for a car to get the governor and his family to the airport.

56
00:06:05,520 --> 00:06:07,590
回纽约一路顺风
Have a safe trip back to New York.

57
00:06:15,070 --> 00:06:19,170
{\an8}情报委员会成员称  康威撒谎

58
00:06:38,630 --> 00:06:39,760
我叫人送来了午餐
I've had lunch brought in.

59
00:06:39,760 --> 00:06:43,330
你肯定挺久没吃过热乎乎的饭菜了
I'm sure it's been quite a while since you've had a hot meal.

60
00:06:44,400 --> 00:06:47,410
-我不会吃的  -你不饿吗
- I won't be eating it. - Aren't you hungry?

61
00:06:48,150 --> 00:06:50,760
我不想受刑的时候吐出来
I don't wanna get sick while I'm being tortured.

62
00:06:50,760 --> 00:06:54,750
没人会给你用刑  请坐吧
No one's getting tortured. Please, have a seat.

63
00:07:07,410 --> 00:07:10,100
你要我叫这些人放了那家人  是吗
You want me to tell these men to release the family, right?

64
00:07:10,360 --> 00:07:12,350
否则  你就得做你必须做的了
If I don't, you'll do what you have to do.

65
00:07:12,350 --> 00:07:14,210
如果我们是那个意思
Oh, if we had any intention of that,

66
00:07:14,220 --> 00:07:16,430
你就不可能离开关塔那摩
you never would have left Guantanamo.

67
00:07:16,710 --> 00:07:18,720
我也不会来这儿
Nor would I be here.

68
00:07:18,720 --> 00:07:19,740
这是哪里
Where is here?

69
00:07:21,890 --> 00:07:24,520
弗吉尼亚州  政府安全屋
Virginia, in a government safe house.

70
00:07:25,940 --> 00:07:26,970
为什么你来
And why you?

71
00:07:27,590 --> 00:07:31,500
出于尊敬  由于事情重大
Out of respect... for the gravity of this situation.

72
00:07:32,730 --> 00:07:35,110
我觉得你是想羞辱我
I think your intention is to humiliate me.

73
00:07:35,980 --> 00:07:37,880
我给你提供了衣服  食物
You've been properly clothed, offered food.

74
00:07:37,880 --> 00:07:39,580
怎么羞辱你了
How are we humiliating you?

75
00:07:41,050 --> 00:07:42,940
我坐在一个女人对面
I'm sitting across from a woman.

76
00:07:46,610 --> 00:07:49,130
没必要装样子了
There's no reason to keep up the facade.

77
00:07:50,440 --> 00:07:52,790
你和你弟弟不是原教旨主义者
You and your brother are not fundamentalists,

78
00:07:52,790 --> 00:07:54,370
也不是叙利亚人
nor are you Syrian.

79
00:07:55,140 --> 00:07:57,150
那是中情局告诉你的吗
This what the CIA's feeding you?

80
00:07:57,720 --> 00:08:01,050
你是伊拉克人  你真名是阿瓦德
You're Iraqi. Your real name is Al Awad.

81
00:08:05,900 --> 00:08:08,330
其实  这上面说你2000年加入了
Actually, it says that you joined 

82
00:08:08,330 --> 00:08:10,090
复兴社会党
the Baath Party in 2000.

83
00:08:10,090 --> 00:08:11,270
你2001年到2002年间是
You were the assistant to the 

84
00:08:11,270 --> 00:08:14,720
基建副部长的助理
undersecretary of infrastructure, 2001, 2002.

85
00:08:14,720 --> 00:08:16,210
随你怎么说
Say whatever you want.

86
00:08:17,110 --> 00:08:20,980
我弟弟会否认  你别想说服除你之外的任何人
My brother will deny. You won't convince anyone but yourselves.

87
00:08:25,410 --> 00:08:26,820
我们驱逐了复兴社会党
We expel the Baathists

88
00:08:26,820 --> 00:08:30,610
你就从官僚变成了极端主义者
and you go from a bureaucrat to an extremist.

89
00:08:31,460 --> 00:08:33,890
但你是个受过高等教育的人  尤瑟夫
But you're a well-educated man, Yusuf...

90
00:08:34,190 --> 00:08:36,970
你才不在乎伊斯兰或哈里发
and you don't care about Islam or the caliphate.

91
00:08:36,970 --> 00:08:39,870
你只是在利用那个刺激士兵情绪
You're just using that to radicalize soldiers.

92
00:08:40,280 --> 00:08:42,970
就像你利用民主和自由那样
Just as you use democracy and freedom.

93
00:08:44,500 --> 00:08:46,640
现在我们理解彼此了
So now we understand each other.

94
00:08:51,240 --> 00:08:54,540
尤瑟夫·艾哈迈德仍被单独监禁在关塔那摩监狱
Yusuf Al Ahmadi remains in solitary confinement in Guantanamo.

95
00:08:54,540 --> 00:08:56,650
如果卡洛琳和梅莉莎·米勒获释
If Caroline and Melissa Miller are released,

96
00:08:56,650 --> 00:09:00,090
我们将允许劫持者在监督下与其联络
we will allow supervised contact with the kidnappers.

97
00:09:00,450 --> 00:09:01,350
马克
Mark.

98
00:09:01,350 --> 00:09:04,530
艾哈迈德一向鼓励这样的恐怖行动
Ahmadi has consistently encouraged acts of terror like this one.

99
00:09:04,530 --> 00:09:06,830
你为什么认为任何的对话
What makes you think that any sort of dialogue

100
00:09:06,830 --> 00:09:08,650
能带来和平的结果
will lead to a peaceful resolution?

101
00:09:08,650 --> 00:09:10,650
要么就完全不建立对话
Well, the alternative is no dialogue at all.

102
00:09:10,660 --> 00:09:12,480
我们想用尽一切办法
We don't wanna leave any stone unturned.

103
00:09:12,930 --> 00:09:14,090
莎拉
Sara.

104
00:09:14,090 --> 00:09:16,080
你是否可以就《华尔街电讯报》的文章
Will you comment on the Wall Street Telegraph article

105
00:09:16,080 --> 00:09:18,150
指出康威州长可能干涉了
about Governor Conway's alleged interference

106
00:09:18,150 --> 00:09:19,570
众议院情报委员会做出评论
with the House Intelligence Committee?

107
00:09:19,570 --> 00:09:23,020
它确认了我们早有怀疑的事
Well, it confirms what we suspected to be true,

108
00:09:23,020 --> 00:09:25,880
但我想你需要的是州长的评论  而非我的
but I think you want the governor's comment, not ours.

109
00:09:25,880 --> 00:09:28,150
沃勒克议员在扭曲事实
Congressman Walleck is misrepresenting events.

110
00:09:28,150 --> 00:09:30,860
-你是说他撒谎了  -我是说他所言不实
- You're saying he lied? - I'm saying he misrepresented.

111
00:09:30,860 --> 00:09:32,970
我在情报委员会有多位朋友
I have a number of friends on the Intelligence Committee,

112
00:09:32,970 --> 00:09:35,900
我是否偶尔跟他们谈话  当然
and do I speak with them sometimes? Of course.

113
00:09:35,900 --> 00:09:37,640
但这跟干涉不是一回事
But that's not the same as interfering.

114
00:09:37,640 --> 00:09:38,800
那么你从未跟委员会成员
So you never discussed the Russia plan

115
00:09:38,800 --> 00:09:39,700
谈论过俄国的计划
with anyone on the committee?

116
00:09:39,700 --> 00:09:40,890
我们或许谈论过
We may have discussed it,

117
00:09:40,890 --> 00:09:43,260
但我又没下达命令
but it's not as though I was issuing orders.

118
00:09:43,260 --> 00:09:46,000
而且我得说  大家现在应该首要关注
And I have to say, everyone's primary focus right now

119
00:09:46,000 --> 00:09:48,200
米勒一家  而非此事
needs to be on the Miller family, not this.

120
00:09:48,200 --> 00:09:49,990
总统是否要求你离开白宫
Did the president ask you to leave the White House?

121
00:09:49,990 --> 00:09:51,740
我们都认为我该做的已经做完
Uh, we agreed that I'd done my part,

122
00:09:51,740 --> 00:09:53,310
其他要靠他了
and that the rest is up to him.

123
00:09:53,310 --> 00:09:55,050
能跟我们谈谈昨晚你跟总统
Can you tell us about your conversation last night

124
00:09:55,050 --> 00:09:56,370
关于艾哈迈德的讨论吗
with the president, regarding Ahmadi?

125
00:09:56,370 --> 00:09:57,830
先说到这儿吧  谢谢大家
That'll be all for now. Thank you so much.

126
00:09:57,830 --> 00:09:58,950
问个问题  先生
Question, sir.

127
00:10:02,520 --> 00:10:03,480
走吧
Let's go.

128
00:10:03,760 --> 00:10:06,770
等等  莉莉的车座还没弄好
Uh, hold on, I'm still fastening Lily's car seat.

129
00:10:08,960 --> 00:10:10,310
-威尔  -别说了
- Will-- - Not a word.

130
00:10:11,740 --> 00:10:13,300
我得说  将军对你说
Well, I have to tell you, the general's apeshit

131
00:10:13,300 --> 00:10:16,720
为自己服役感到羞耻暴跳如雷
over what you said about being ashamed of your service.

132
00:10:17,520 --> 00:10:18,400
他可能会接受采访
He may talk to the press.

133
00:10:18,400 --> 00:10:20,410
没想出如何合适地回应这堆狗屁
Nobody does any press until we have a proper response

134
00:10:20,410 --> 00:10:21,510
谁都不许接受采访
to all this shit.

135
00:10:21,510 --> 00:10:24,100
爸爸说了  "狗屁"   狗屁  狗屁
Daddy said "Shit." Shit, shit, shit!

136
00:10:24,100 --> 00:10:25,050
住口
Stop it!

137
00:10:25,840 --> 00:10:27,120
你得给我挖到沃勒克的把柄
You need to bring me something on Walleck.

138
00:10:27,130 --> 00:10:28,700
我们得让他信誉扫地
We need to discredit him.

139
00:10:28,700 --> 00:10:30,720
-弄好了没有  -你不用冲我们撒火
- Are you done yet? - You don't need to snap at us.

140
00:10:30,720 --> 00:10:32,400
-好了没有  -好了
- Are you done yet? - Yes.

141
00:10:32,400 --> 00:10:33,610
快走  马上
Let's go. Now.

142
00:10:35,470 --> 00:10:37,070
那是如果他们获释
That's if they're released.

143
00:10:37,070 --> 00:10:39,230
等我们了解了具体情况会把空白处补上
We'll fill in the blanks once we have details.

144
00:10:41,150 --> 00:10:42,760
这是为最糟糕的情况准备的
This is if the worst happens.

145
00:10:48,240 --> 00:10:49,600
耶茨写的吗
Yates wrote these?

146
00:10:50,550 --> 00:10:53,240
不  我先写了个底
No, I... I took a stab at it first.

147
00:10:57,510 --> 00:10:59,030
另外  汤姆·汉默施密特打来了
Also, Tom Hammerschmidt called.

148
00:10:59,030 --> 00:11:00,140
他想采访总统
He wants an interview with the president.

149
00:11:00,140 --> 00:11:01,650
不肯说是什么事
He wouldn't say what for.

150
00:11:03,540 --> 00:11:05,190
他现在是哪家的
What outlet is he with now?

151
00:11:05,690 --> 00:11:08,840
他回《先驱报》了  说给你发了邮件
He's back at the Herald. Said he emailed you directly.

152
00:11:18,340 --> 00:11:24,540
{\an8}雷米·丹顿  杰姬·夏普和加勒特·沃克均已公开作证

153
00:11:26,460 --> 00:11:27,600
让我单独待会儿
I need the room.

154
00:11:29,430 --> 00:11:30,480
都出去
Everyone out.

155
00:11:36,790 --> 00:11:37,850
接《先驱报》
Get me the Herald.

156
00:11:39,740 --> 00:11:41,010
汤姆·汉默施密特
Tom Hammerschmidt.

157
00:11:41,200 --> 00:11:44,560
这里有个手机信号塔
Well, there's a cell tower here.

158
00:11:44,570 --> 00:11:46,620
一般流量不多
Uh, typically very low traffic,

159
00:11:46,630 --> 00:11:49,690
但在来电期间有增加
but it showed higher usage during the time of the call,

160
00:11:49,700 --> 00:11:51,550
尤其是东南天线
especially the southeastern antenna.

161
00:11:51,550 --> 00:11:53,980
那么我们应该能定位热点  锁定位置
So we should be able to ping the hotspot, zero in?

162
00:11:53,980 --> 00:11:55,500
信号塔很多
Eh, it's hundreds of tower faces.

163
00:11:55,500 --> 00:11:56,620
我能说出大致区域
I can give you the general area,

164
00:11:56,620 --> 00:11:57,980
具体定位要更久
but pinpointing will take longer.

165
00:11:57,980 --> 00:11:59,690
而且我无法保证肯定是他们
I can't even guarantee it's gonna be them.

166
00:11:59,690 --> 00:12:01,720
分析每一座塔
I want every one of those towers analyzed.

167
00:12:01,720 --> 00:12:04,630
专注分析背景环境噪声会更有收效
Well, we're better off concentrating on ambient background sound.

168
00:12:04,640 --> 00:12:07,160
如果我能把那个跟
If I can match that to other calls made

169
00:12:07,160 --> 00:12:09,130
这一带的其他通话做匹配
in this area around the same time as--

170
00:12:09,130 --> 00:12:10,500
我不是在问你的建议
I'm not asking your advice.

171
00:12:10,500 --> 00:12:12,510
我是告诉你该做什么
I'm telling you what I want you to do.

172
00:12:12,510 --> 00:12:14,230
分析信号塔数据
Focus on the tower data.

173
00:12:16,470 --> 00:12:17,960
